15:35:30.000Z","msg":"智能電話於2009年咁上下開始普及。<br />\n之前仲係Sony Ericsson 盛行嘅年代，個個中意佢有金屬感同聽歌一流。當然電話可以上網當電腦用真係匪夷所思，開頭都只係得班白領用black Berry。<br />\n<br />\n到咗iPhone 3開始出現，就個個都買。個個當係熱潮咁買同炒，當時邊有人諗到電話都要排隊先買到，仲要炒到成萬蚊。由大人到大學生，個個都用iPhone。之後Samsung 就有樣學樣炒蘋果，結果同對方瓜分電話市場。之前龍頭Sony 同Nokia 等等都要退落黎。<br />\n<br />\n成個過程都只係兩三年，幾乎主流嘅香港人都換哂智能電話，成為低頭族。以前返工時間人人睇報紙嘅景象慢慢消失，大家都低頭睇戲或打機。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"講真，咩Uber 美團，騰信，呢個世界好多用app既公司都要多謝教主"},{"pid":"1d407248f38cf5a576b4dea125155d8cb98c0fa5","tid":1147068,"uid":80148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"屋企仲有部I-phone4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8857a851be0387ae9ff1939ff1d4dd1ba992f532","tid":1147068,"uid":43314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T02:56:38.000Z","msg":"唔見咗部 iPhone 3g，無耐換咗 Nexus one 食正寫 Android app 條 水，自此改變命運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585b61b8e1a955c86da1c9b866688f6e8a79da07","tid":1147068,"uid":45252,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"其實iPhone都唔係第一部smartphone...<br />\n我之前已經有用Nokia同Samsung嘅smartphone，仲有Facebook同WhatsApp"},{"pid":"e51086fb989aba7d3d26cbbbab482f159cec833b","tid":1147068,"uid":33059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T03:08:36.000Z","msg":"無iPhone 都無lihkg"},{"pid":"8f073ce447bc7a26bbd6de8ffc36c4733011253e","tid":1147068,"uid":19789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"585b61b8e1a955c86da1c9b866688f6e8a79da07","tid":1147068,"uid":45252,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"其實iPhone都唔係第一部smartphone...<br />\n我之前已經有用Nokia同Samsung嘅smartphone，仲有Facebook同WhatsApp"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"問題係冇人記得<br />\n搞到做第一部都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji